data.description: Introducing this delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence, nestled on a sprawling city lot spanning three parcels that is fully fenced in. Tons of natural light fills this spacious home, with a welcoming front porch that invites you to enjoy the view of the outdoors from within. Notable updates include a brand-new roof, complete with a transferable 50-year warranty. Fresh paint, modernized windows, and a revamped kitchen add a touch of modern charm. With all these improvements and a move-in-ready status, this home is ready for its new owner to make it their own. Lower level fireplace is for looks only.
